<footer class="footer">
  <div class="content has-text-centered">
    <p>
      <strong>Pawesome Care</strong> by <a href="https://jgthms.com">Zeina Hares, Michael McCabe and Adam Day</a>. Proud members of the Dog and Cat Spotting Society
